         AnnotationDbi, BiocParallel, Biostrings (>= 2.33.11),
         GenomeInfoDb (>= 1.3.6), GenomicRanges (>= 1.19.13),
         GenomicFeatures, Rsamtools (>= 1.17.8), BSgenome, Gviz, shiny
Suggests: BiocStyle, org.Hs.eg.db, BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg19,
          TxDb.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg19.knownGene, SNPlocs.Hsapiens.dbSNP.20120608,
